[[feedback:prt3]]]]></text>
    </questiontext>
    <generalfeedback format="html">
      <text><![CDATA[<p>By the key point, the equation of a circle with centre at \((\alpha,\beta)\) and radius \(r\) is \((x-\alpha)^2+(y-\beta)^2 = r^2\).</p>

<p>Circle A has centre \(({@c1[1]@},{@c1[2]@})\), and radius \({@r1@}\), hence A has equation:</p>
\[{@ta1@}.\]
<p>Circle B has centre \(({@c2[1]@},{@c2[2]@})\), and radius \({@r2@}\), hence B has equation:</p>
\[{@ta2@}.\]
<p>Circle C has centre \(({@c3[1]@},{@c3[2]@})\), and radius \({@r3@}\), hence C has equation:</p>
\[{@ta3@}.\]]]></text>
    </generalfeedback>
